Package org.gbif.doi.service.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DoiException
    Any exception happening during requests with agency APIs will be converted to this exception.
    DoiExistsException
    Happening when trying to reserve or register an existing DOI.
    DoiHttpException
    Happening when there are some problems on DataCite side (service responded with an HTTP error).
    DoiNotFoundException
    Happening when trying to delete or update a non-existing DOI.
    InvalidMetadataException
    Exception thrown if the used (datacite) metadata was not valid.
